  61:				;
  62:				; The entry point for the BIOS is at offset BIOS_STARTUP, but we must allow for
  63:				; the missing first entry ("BOOT") and the start address of the BIOS. The include
  64:				; file is written more for use within CP/M, where this format makes more sense.
