 195:				;
 196:				;
 197:				; Allocate memory pages. Pages are named "CPM0", "CPM1" ... "CPMZ". The page
 198:				; numbers will be returned starting at the base address specified. These are
 199:				; one for each bank in the 64 kB space.
 200:				; Returns with carry set on error. Call with:
 201:				; A - number of pages required
 202:				; HL - base address for list of page numbers
 203:				; Returns with carry set if request cannot be met.
 204:  734+11	00A3' C5      	cpmem           push bc
